Q1: What happen if thread-count="2" in testng is less than the no. of methods i.e 3 present in class?
Ans: In this case two methods will run on same Thread-ID. 

Q2: How to configure to run single method on multiple thread-count?
Ans: By Using these three attribute:
			threadPoolSize = 3,
			invocationCount = 3, 
			timeOut = 1000
			
